CC0 1.0 Universal Public Domain Dedication

To the extent possible under law, the contributors dedicate the original
compilation content in this repository to the public domain under CC0 1.0
Universal.

This dedication applies only to original compilation content created for this
project, including review notes, taxonomies, screening decisions, extraction
forms, normalized registers, and repository/source audit metadata.

It does not apply to third-party code, papers, abstracts, source text, cloned
repositories, database exports, logos, trademarks, or any other material not
owned by the contributors. Those materials remain under their original terms.

